Bigger signages to help passengers at KLIA, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Bigger signages to help passengers at KLIA, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
