<HEADLINE>
Brighter street lights to check vice at Taiping Lake Gardens, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Brighter street lights to check vice at Taiping Lake Gardens, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
