<HEADLINE>
Tk 13,600 cr ADP, THE INDEPENDENT
</HEADLINE>
Tk 13,600 cr ADP, THE INDEPENDENT &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   THE INDEPENDENT
   BANGLADESH
   ENGLISH
