<HEADLINE>
Practice of safe custody challenged, THE INDEPENDENT
</HEADLINE>
Practice of safe custody challenged, THE INDEPENDENT &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   THE INDEPENDENT
   BANGLADESH
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

<TEXT>
WASHINGTON, D.C. 20003 Tel: 202-547-4512 Fax: 202-546-4194
