	   IPOH, Thurs. - The City Council plans to turn two prime lots
into multi- storey car parks to ease the acute shortage.
	   The proposed projects are in Jalan Osborne, behind the Majestic
Cinema, and Jalan Datuk Onn Jaafar, behind the Ocean Supermarket,
city councillor Lee Heng said today.
