Education Ministry to go ahead with scheme, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Education Ministry to go ahead with scheme, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
   Noor Adzman BaharuddinASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

