	   Tonight ... Wind east to southeast 10 to 15 kt. Seas 3 to 4 ft.
Scattered showers.
	   Saturday ... Wind southeast to east 10 to 15 kt. Seas 3 to 4 ft.
Widely scattered showers. 	   
