<BODY>
<SLUG> RUBBER sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Rubber, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Rubber, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
