	   RECENTLY, I went to watch the movie ``Godzilla'' at Rex Cinema
in Kuala Lumpur, and it was a nightmare for me.
	   Somebody put bubble gum on my chair. Seated at the back of me
were some children and beside me were two adults. So I do not know
who put it there.
	   It is high time bubble gum was banned in public places. It is
already banned in Singapore because people use it to jam the lifts
in high-rise buildings.
	   
