<SLUG> FOUR-NABBED-AFTER-HEIST sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Four nabbed after heist at electrical shop, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Four nabbed after heist at electrical shop, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 11, 1998
