<HEADLINE>
Selangor to meet Negri, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Selangor to meet Negri, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 11, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

