	   LEAGUE champions Selangor are drawn to play third placed Negri
Sembilan in the semifinals of the Malaysian Cricket Association Cup
Final on June 12- 14 at the PKNS ground in Petaling Jaya.
	   In the other semifinals, league runnerup Malaysian Malays will
meet Johor at the Royal Selangor Club in Bukit Kiara.
	   Fixtures - MCA Cup s-finals: June 12-14 Selangor v Negri (PKNS,
Kelana Jaya); Malaysian Malays v Johor (RSC, Bukit Kiara).
	   June 19-21: Final (PKNS/Kilat Club - yet to be confirmed).
	   Div Two - semifinals June 12: Terengganu v Johor (Batu
Cantonment); Manza v Selangor (KTJ, Mantin).
	   June 14 - 3rd-4th placing (Batu Cantonment); Final (KTJ,
Mantin).
	   
