Australia, has already registerd two wins and two thirds in seven
outings. He last won when beating Supreme Fever in the Class 3, Div
2 - 1200m at Bukit Timah in March.
	   Last week, Ocean Front set the pace before finishing eighth to
Full Of Action in the Class 2, Div 2 - 1200m in yielding going.
	   Ocean Front, trained by Wilming Yeo, has benefitted from the run
and should give a better showing this week.
