	   THE Kluang District Annual athletics meet will have 400 athletes
participating at the Kluang Stadium on June 21.
	   According to Klang AAA secretary R.S. Nair, the one-day meet
would serve as trials to select the district contingent for the
coming Johor Athletic championship this year.
	   Nair added the coaching and selection committees would be on the
lookout at the district meet for athletes to be drafted into the
district training squad.
	   Interested athletes can call Nair at Tel: 07-7723197 for
information.
	   
