<HEADLINE>
Workers urge U.S. to lobby IMF on loans, JAKARTA POST
</HEADLINE>
Workers urge U.S. to lobby IMF on loans, JAKARTA POST &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   JAKARTA POST
   INDONESIA
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

