SPK-Sentosa deeper into the red, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
SPK-Sentosa deeper into the red, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
