<BODY>
<SLUG> GAZETTE-LAND-FOR sked </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Gazette land for agriculture, Perak urged, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Gazette land for agriculture, Perak urged, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
