Exploiting ex-mining sites, idle padi fields, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Exploiting ex-mining sites, idle padi fields, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
