Dr Ling fails to get more costs from Kit Siang, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Dr Ling fails to get more costs from Kit Siang, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
