<HEADLINE>
Smart finding shortest route, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Smart finding shortest route, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
