<HEADLINE>
40 quizzed by police over bodies found in car, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
40 quizzed by police over bodies found in car, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 12, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
