<HEADLINE>
World Cup: Dugarry leads dominating 3-0 French victory
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; EDS: DELETES extraneous word from lead. &QL; 
 &UR; By RAF CASERT &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   MARSEILLE, France (AP) _ With three goals and repeated attacks,
France produced the result the whole host nation had been hoping
for and crushed South Africa 3-0 to stake its claim as a World Cup
favorite.
