  GRANDE DE ARECIBO AND ITS TRIBUTARIES...AS WELL AS LOW LYING
  AREAS.

  DON'T DRIVE INTO AREAS WHERE WATER COVERS THE ROAD.  MOST CARS
  WILL BE WASHED AWAY BY LESS THAN TWO FEET OF RUNNING WATER!
