	   WORLD SPORTS AT 0000 GMT
 &UR; WORLD CUP:
	   PARIS _ The first red card, the first scoreless draw, the first
team to score three goals. Almost the first World Cup goal by a
goalkeeper. Oh, and another own goal.
	   Slug Sports-Soccer-World Cup Roundup. Recap expected by 0200
GMT.
	   By Robert Millward.
	   MARSEILLE, France _ France produces that whiff of champagne
soccer the whole host nation had been hoping for, crushing South
Africa 3-0 to raise hopes it can go all the way in the World Cup.
	   Slug Sports-Soccer-France-South Africa. Recap expected by 0200
GMT.
	   By Raf Casert.
